Hosting relevant 1962 Local Government election results and other datasets
*NOTICE OF UPDATE (1/4/2026)*
- Added 1962 Perak and Johor Election Result Outcome
*NOTICE OF UPDATE (2/4/2026)*
- Added 1962 Summarised Vote Tallies and Seat Distribution.
- Tindak Malaysia doesn't vouch for the accuracy of Election Commission reporting and there are serious mismatches of the data between Election Commission Report and Tindak Malaysia's computation
- Readers are to read the metadata to understand discrepancies arising before making any judgements on Summarised Vote Tallies and Seat Distribution
- Two council data for Kelantan is missing
*NOTICE OF UPDATE (4/4/2026)*
- Closed gaps for missing Kelantan two council data (Dabong and Pauh Lima Councils)
- Updated summarised tallies for Tindak Malaysia vote and seat distribution, updated metadata and other sources file and added 1962 Local Government Election Details
